        <p>Span, linear combinations, and linear independence/dependence.</p>
<div class="toc">
<ul>
<li><a href="#span">1 Span</a><ul>
<li><a href="#finite-and-infinite-dimensions">1.1 Finite and infinite dimensions</a></li>
